# Welcome to Islamorada Landing Page

A simple and responsive landing page showcasing **Islamorada**, voted #1 place in the Florida Keys. This project was created to practice HTML, CSS, and responsive design using the SheCodes Responsive course.

---

## Table of Contents

- [About](#about)  
- [Features](#features)  
- [Sections](#sections)  
- [Gallery](#gallery)  
- [Footer](#footer)  
- [Installation](#installation)  
- [Usage](#usage)  
- [Credits](#credits)  

---

## About

Islamorada is a beautiful village in the Florida Keys known as the **Sportfishing Capital of the World**. This landing page highlights its attractions, activities, and culture.

The page is fully responsive and built with HTML5 and CSS3.

---

## Features

- Responsive layout with CSS Grid and Flexbox
- Google Maps embeds for top attractions
- Instagram post embeds for a gallery
- External links to official sites for more information
- Clean, minimal design using Google Fonts

---

## Sections

### Header
- Title and tagline: ".ISLAMORADA."
- Main headline: "VOTED #1 PLACE IN THE FLORIDA KEYS"
- Subheadline: "THAT EVERY TOURIST SHOULD VISIT"
- Learn more link to [Islamorada official site](https://www.islamorada.fl.us/382/About-Us)

### Why Islamorada?
- Section explaining why Islamorada is a top destination
- Includes an image of a dock and descriptive text
- Highlights outdoor lifestyle, coral reefs, and cultural history

### Top Things to Do
- Three featured attractions:
  1. **Rain Barrel Village**
     - Open-air shopping destination with tropical gardens and handmade crafts
     - [Learn more](https://rainbarrelvillage.com/)
  2. **Founders Park**
     - Community park with beach, pool, sports courts, and events
     - [Learn more](https://www.islamorada.fl.us/249/Founders-Park)
  3. **Marathon Bagel at Islamorada**
     - Authentic New York-style bagels in the Florida Keys
     - [Learn more](https://marathonbagelco.com/)

- Each attraction includes:
  - Image
  - Google Maps iframe
  - Description, address, and notable highlights

### Gallery
- Instagram embeds displaying photos from Islamorada

### Footer
- More about Islamorada: maps, transport, and directions
- About the Florida Keys
- About this website and project

